dataList.content: Queequeg... I don't...! I don't want to let you go... Not you...!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: It's all because of you, Ishmael!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: This happened because you dared to unearth her buried heart! Because you forced her broken heart into the open!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: The fault lies with you once again, Ishmael!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: Look at what you've done. Watch her determination crumble, her conviction collapse. Now, with her faith broken, the pale claims Queequeg!
